    "desc": "Official portal website of the City of Amsterdam, with everything you need to visit, enjoy, live, work, invest and do business in the Amsterdam Metropolitan Area. ",
    "navbar": "MENU",
    "text": "Consent\nDetails\nAbout\nThis website uses cookies\nWe use cookies to personalise content and ads, to provide social media features and to analyse our traffic. We also share information about your use of our site with our social media, advertising and analytics partners who may combine it with other information that you’ve provided to them or that they’ve collected from your use of their services.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDeny\nCustomize\nAllow all\nPowered by Cookiebot by Usercentrics\n.st0{fill:#FD000D;} .st1{fill:#FFFFFF;}\nMENU\nLANGUAGES\nORDER YOUR I AMSTERDAM CITY CARD\nWelcome to Amsterdam\nTop 20 things to do in Amsterdam\nExplore Amsterdam's best kept secrets\nExplore Amsterdam's cultural agenda\nYour guide to the Amsterdam Area\nTravel and stay\nPlanning a trip to Amsterdam? Find all the resources you need to get started - from accommodation and excursions to renting a car or using public transport.\nSee and do\nWith world-class museums, quirky festivals, theatre, live music, laid-back bars and delightful restaurants, there's never a shortage of things to do in Amsterdam!\nLiving in Amsterdam\nLook up official information for internationals on living, studying and working in the Amsterdam Area.\nStart a business in Amsterdam\nBe part of a thriving business ecosystem – alongside cutting-edge startups, international corporations and innovative entrepreneurs.\nOrganise a meeting in Amsterdam\nAmsterdam is the ideal destination for your next business meeting, conference or event.\nOur platforms\nOrder the I amsterdam City Card\nThe I amsterdam City Card includes a public transport pass, a detailed city map and provides over 50 free and 60 discounted offers.\nREAD MORE\nRead the latest I amsterdam City Guide\nI amsterdam City Guide is Amsterdam’s city magazine, packed full of insider tips for what to do and see in the city.\nREAD MORE\nFind out more about Amsterdam\nSearch\nABOUT US\namsterdam & partners\nAdvertise with us\nPress & media\nContact\nOUR NETWORK\nI amsterdam City Card\nMunicipal government\nIN Amsterdam\nStartupAmsterdam\nI AMSTERDAM WEBSHOP\nGifts\nTypical Amsterdam\nLocal Makers\nTravel & Outdoor\nFACEBOOK\nTWITTER\nINSTAGRAM\nPINTEREST\nLINKEDIN\n© 2023 I amsterdam Disclaimer Privacy statement Recommendation algorithms Change cookie settings",
